s}em{\textgreater}GOES-12{\textless}/em{\textgreater} OT detections are compared with objective Eddy Dissipation Rate Turbulence and National Lightning Detection Network observations to show the strong relationship among OTs, aviation turbulence, and cloud-to-ground lightning activity.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}{\textless}/section{\textgreater}},
